[[File:Knife detail.png|left|120px]]
A '''knife''' is a tool used for a large variety of tasks, mostly for fletching [[logs]] in the [[Fletching]] skill. This is also an excellent tool for cutting through webs, especially to the [[Mage Arena]] in the deep [[Wilderness]]. Check out the '''spawns''' section to find out where knives spawn in the game. They are also sold in [[general store]]s in the [[Shantay Pass]] and [[Catherby]], at [[Trader Stan's Trading Post]] on [[Karamja]], or the [[Ardougne Spice Stall]].

==Uses==
Uses for knives include but are not limited to:
*Shaping logs in the [[Fletching]] skill.
*Slashing webs. (Note: As opposed to the knife, the [[Wilderness sword 1]] or better has a 100% success-rate)
*Slicing and dicing [[orange]]s, [[lime]]s, [[banana]]s, [[lemon]]s, and [[pineapple]]s in the [[Cooking]] skill.
*Cutting cacti in the [[Kharidian Desert]] to fill [[waterskin]]s.
*Chopping up such things as [[tuna]], [[sweetcorn]], and [[tomatoes]] into [[bowl]]s.
*Hollowing [[calquat]]s to form [[calquat keg]]s.
*Scraping off sap from some types of [[tree]]s while having a [[bucket]] in the inventory to make a [[bucket of sap]].
*Making [[chocolate dust]] by using it on a [[chocolate bar]].
*Cutting a fish using [[Barbarian Training]] in [[Baxtorian Falls]] to obtain various parts of the fish with multiple uses.
*Setting up deadfall traps in the [[Hunter]] skill.
*Dissecting [[sacred eel]]s to extract [[zulrah's scales]].

